" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Listeria monocytogenes in cerebrospinal fluid",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 360px; height: 322px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Gram stain of cerebrospinal fluid (x1000) shows inflammatory cells and small, gram-positive rods and coccobacilli. Culture of this specimen revealed moderate-sized, beta-hemolytic colonies composed of small, motile gram-positive rods, confirmed to be",
